OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome late
OL,6,Fsunny spells, especially in south and
OL,7,Feast, but cloud increasing through the
OL,8,Fevening with outbreaks of mainly light
OL,9,Frain spreading southeast. The rain
OL,10,Fclears around dawn and the cloud
OL,11,Fbreaks.
OL,12,
OL,13,CMonday:FAny remaining overnight rain
OL,14,Fin south soon clearing the a dry day
OL,15,Fwith some good spells of sunshine.
OL,16,FCloudier again in evening with a
OL,17,Flittle rain in west.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
