OL,3,GNorthern Ireland
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FEarly
OL,6,Frain on Tuesday then sunny spells and
OL,7,Fshowers. Rather cold Wednesday with
OL,8,Fheavy showers and occasionally strong
OL,9,Fnorthwesterly winds, the showers and
OL,10,Fwinds easing on Thursday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
